            <div class="space-y-16">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase">Engineering Assistant <span class="text-brand-purple text-sm ml-4 font-mono">2025 – Present</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Keith Engineering [cite: 180-182]</p>
                    <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
                        <li>• Assisted in equipment reconditioning evaluation and quoting process[cite: 183].</li>
                        <li>• Performed CAD modelling, BOM creation, and quality assurance checks[cite: 184].</li>
                        <li>• Prepared project costing and customer quotes for various spare parts[cite: 185].</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase">Shift Supervisor <span class="text-brand-purple text-sm ml-4 font-mono">2021 – Present</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-6">Lord Dudley Hotel [cite: 192-194]</p>
