                        <li>• Managed over $4,000 in nightly sales and supervised up to 20 staff members[cite: 195, 197].</li>
                        <li>• Developed adaptability and high-pressure team leadership skills [cite: 227-229].</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-gray-50 p-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 border border-gray-100">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-brand-orange font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] mb-6">Technical Skills [cite: 214-215]</h3>
                <ul class="text-[11px] space-y-3 font-mono uppercase text-gray-600">
